com.namics.commons.random.generator

Interface RandomGenerator<SupportedType>

  • Type Parameters:
    SupportedType - Type that can be created with this Generator.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractGenericCollectionGenerator, ArrayListGenerator, BigDecimalGenerator, BigIntegerGenerator, BooleanGenerator, ByteGenerator, CalendarGenerator, DateGenerator, DateTimeGenerator, DoubleGenerator, FloatGenerator, HashMapGenerator, HashSetGenerator, IntegerGenerator, JodaPeriodGenerator, LocalDateGenerator, LocalDateTimeGenerator, LocaleGenerator, LocalTimeGenerator, LongGenerator, StringGenerator, TreeMapGenerator, TreeSetGenerator, UriGenerator, UrlGenerator, ZonedDateTimeGenerator

    public interface RandomGenerator<SupportedType>
    Interface to be Implemented to add a custom RandomGenerator for a custom SupportedType. The generator can be registered in several ways:
  • automatically when placed in same package as the SupportedType
  • Manually by registering either class or instance directly to RandomData.addRandomGenerator(com.namics.commons.random.generator.RandomGenerator)
  • Manually by registering package for scanning to RandomData.addRandomGenerators(String)
